{"type": "article", "id": 20361, "title": "带有交叉纹路的托盘", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-07T07:36:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110602x5HRBKla81XMroTb.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套用钢丝制作的托盘，由一个长方形和两个正方形组成。托盘中间是斜向的纹路，两者重叠在一起正好组成交叉纹，移动放在里面的小托盘还会产生纹路的变化，看似简单，却也有生活的乐趣。托盘是灰色的，在此基础上可以选择偏蓝、绿、黄等多种不同的色调，售价 179 欧元起，<a href=\"http://www.roije.com/index.php?route=product/product&amp;product_id=80\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110600Opejf8UnDKqXFLWz.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"441\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.735\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070211060167VbkPaiOfj3y8Sh.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021106019tWKXEu5OLjoITC2.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"451\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110602c4nJ2hu9BrsOVowk.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}